Package com.distrimind.bouncycastle.pqc.math.linearalgebra

Class GF2Matrix

java.lang.Object
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.pqc.math.linearalgebra.Matrix
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.pqc.math.linearalgebra.GF2Matrix
public class GF2Matrix extends Matrix
This class describes some operations with matrices over finite field GF(2) and is used in ecc and MQ-PKC (also has some specific methods and implementation)
